    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The only relevant question about Al Gore's choice of Joseph I. Lieberman as his running mate (front page, Aug. 8) is what effect a Jewish vice president might have on Middle East policy.</p>
        <p>MIKE LILES JR.  Seattle, Aug. 8, 2000</p>
